---
import PublicLayout from '../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
import ProblemCard from '../../components/ProblemCard.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="How We Help"
  description="smagile helps teams through consultancy, facilitation, and practical agile training. We meet you where you are."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">How we help</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
      Every team and organisation is different. We do not offer a one-size-fits-all package.
      Instead, we listen to your challenges and tailor our support to your context.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8">
      <ProblemCard
        problem="We need someone to work alongside our teams and help them improve"
        solution="Our consultancy and facilitation service embeds alongside your teams. We observe, coach, and facilitate to help them find their own path to better outcomes."
        href="/how-we-help/consultancy/"
        linkText="Consultancy and facilitation"
      />
      <ProblemCard
        problem="Our people need practical training they can apply straight away"
        solution="We are licensed ProKanban.org trainers and deliver bespoke agile fundamentals training built on over a decade of real-world experience."
        href="/how-we-help/training/"
        linkText="Explore training options"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about" class="relative bg-primary dark:bg-grey-800 py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-dark/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white font-heading">About smagile</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 w-16 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-light to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-white/85 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          smagile is a remote-first agile consultancy offering specialist support to product teams,
          along with training and coaching for professionals working in agile environments.
        </p>
        <p>
          Founded by James Farley, an agile consultant with over a decade of experience supporting
          product teams of varying degrees of maturity. James is a licensed
          <a href="https://prokanban.org" class="text-accent-light hover:text-accent underline underline-offset-2" rel="noopener noreferrer">ProKanban.org</a>
          trainer, accredited to teach the application of Professional Kanban.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe in meeting teams where they are. There is no single framework or methodology
          that fits every context. Instead, we listen, observe, and work alongside your people to
          find what works for them.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-3.5 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all border border-white/20 hover:border-white/30"
        >
          Let's talk about your challenges
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
